{"tid":857940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天津已全面停售普通汽油 改用乙醇汽油 2020年起將推行至全國","createTime":"2018-10-11T12:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T05:24:06.000Z","uid":48083,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"98c6b2e1e1cf0443750dd1e65656ff0c6d258478","tid":857940,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"車查查<br />\n10-08 22:37<br />\n10月1日起，天津宣佈全面停售普通無鉛汽油，改用乙醇汽油。據統計，遼寧、吉林、黑龍江、河南、安徽等11省已全部或部分使用乙醇汽油，按國家政策，2020年起，全國所有地區全部普及乙醇汽油。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/202120_ce39704885633f7c247ceaf6fb645af1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F202120_ce39704885633f7c247ceaf6fb645af1.png&h=1ea4136a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sohu.com/a/258271578_358259/?pvid=000115_3w_a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sohu.com%2Fa%2F258271578_358259%2F%3Fpvid%3D000115_3w_a&d=diPzZA6xL86YPXKEDuBT8MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1ff1d8fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.sohu.com/a/258271578_358259/?pvid=000115_3w_a</a>"},{"pid":"4391f389455727df3ce90d0efb303487ffd442f5","tid":857940,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"無貨鳥"},{"pid":"806707bfb19c71dda586815f69eb7e0aa548b2d3","tid":857940,"uid":156363,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"乙醇好易吸到濕氣，同濃度會揮發降低，仲有濃度高既話又會傷金屬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d14c2286e8562364199e0ffece5b6a8e2934e1","tid":857940,"uid":62646,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:30:37.000Z","msg":"停止左進口美國石油丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67d43fc0a1ad387590884305a02e08bd9ba8d50","tid":857940,"uid":39855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":