-11T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"但強國高粱都要進口<br />\n<br />\n係咩玩法"},{"pid":"5e45202d592d7bd809a5ba8aab1daf8023427e63","tid":857940,"uid":140538,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"fc7761ae5ee559fbc1a4f7f29a800133bffe3275","tid":857940,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:36:04.000Z","msg":"中國豬戒黃豆<br />\n中國車戒汽油<br />\n中國2025 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"支那人話得就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不要說三道四<br />\n<br />\n長征沒汽柴油怎用發電機？ 老紅軍：我們用豬油<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2576230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2576230&d=diPzZA6xL86YPXKEDuBT8MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c640a1f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2576230&h=18912ca1\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2576230</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php7OURBa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php7OURBa.jpg&h=dfc4e50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國10月7日是「十一長假」最後一天，各官媒爭相做出國慶系列報導，有的甚至重溫過去的國慶專題節目，其中一段影片，高齡99歲的「老紅軍」指出，在長征路上發電機沒有汽油用就用柴油，沒有柴油我們「用的是豬油」，網友不可置信，諷刺說「一本正經的胡說八道」！<br />\n<br />\n中國《央視》節目片段中，這名身穿紅衛兵衣服的長者在鏡頭前說道：「充電機要用汽油，沒有汽油了可以用柴油，沒有柴油那個時候我們在長征路上，用的是豬油」。"},{"pid":"62a5fef3f3b2b9e98e14f3af0f00fceec1968319","tid":857940,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"806707bfb19c71dda586815f69eb7e0aa548b2d3","tid":857940,"uid":156363,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"乙醇好易吸到濕氣，同濃度會揮發降低，仲有濃度高既話又會傷金屬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:44:33.000Z","msg":"肯定益自己友啦<img src=\"/assets/fa